data.description: Back to market due to buyer finance failed. Excellent condition raised ranch style single  house with 3 bedrooms, 3 renovated full bathrooms.  Open floor plan. New Kitchen with granite countertop. New roof,  New engineering hardwood floor on the main floor. Waterproof vinyl floor in the fully finished basement with Large recreation room and office room.   Fresh paint.  Large deck on the back and side for your entertainment.  Very convenient location to Route 2, 10, 95, 97, 100 and tons of local shopping and restaurants!  Must see it.
